# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Local dev → shared staging (Sub-1). These OVERRIDE the docker-compose values
# above when developing against the shared Postgres/Redis/MinIO directly
# (e.g. on the server, or a laptop via Tailscale SSH local-forward).
# Real values live in the gitignored .env / .env.devlocal — never commit them.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://interlab_staging01:<DB_PASSWORD>@127.0.0.1:5440/interlab_db_staging
# REDIS_URL=redis://:<REDIS_PASSWORD>@127.0.0.1:6380
# MINIO_ENDPOINT=http://127.0.0.1:9101            # global MinIO (console port published; S3 API may be internal-only)
# MINIO_ACCESS_KEY=<minio-access-key>
# MINIO_SECRET_KEY=<minio-secret-key>
# MINIO_BUCKET_ATTACHMENTS=interlab-private
# MINIO_BUCKET_AVATARS=interlab-public

# Seed account passwords — consumed once by scripts/seed.js, then bcrypt-hashed.
# If unset, all 8 accounts fall back to DEMO_PASSWORD.
# SEED_PW_SUPERADMIN=
# SEED_PW_CEO=
# SEED_PW_SALES=
# SEED_PW_ADMINLOG=
# SEED_PW_FINANCE=
# SEED_PW_TECHNICAL=
# SEED_PW_HRGA=
# SEED_PW_TAX=